{"tid":1711279,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔好將政治撈埋ACG]「成為小說家吧」與中國公司合辦小說大賞條件引網友吐槽","createTime":"2019-11-12T10:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T14:26:28.000Z","uid":33798,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1435d7b48b3e0b55ef92a4380a5eb4b6d59fc122","tid":1711279,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T10:52:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9EXsZdd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9EXsZdd.png&h=2bae55e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近中國公司「金科文化」聯同「成為小說家吧」舉辦的「JINKE小説大賞」活動<br />\n這個「JINKE小説大賞」的大賞作除了能獲得30萬日元，作品還會在中國影像化<br />\n正因為大賞作會在中國市場影像化，所以除了希望作品避免有必須要大場面CG的內容，還有一些讓日本網友一看就忍不住要吐槽的避免事項：<br />\n・表明政治立場<br />\n・反映現實政治的題材<br />\n・在異世界展開第二次人生等<br />\n・幽靈・違反社會觀念的戀愛(師生戀、同性戀、兄弟姊妹戀等)・太過獵奇、黑暗、暴力的題材<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/93734/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F93734%2F&d=9CaroZtPfqcCLVRp0XVEkYlS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=0e64f7ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/93734/</a><br />\n<br />\n班政治潔癖滿意未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab2ee72a2dd2df7b3ed954ef4e75304e13e45b51","tid":1711279,"uid":76854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:07:44.000Z","msg":"冇記錯成為小說家吧好似最多異世界作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67efdc1b0d6a5cedb974d2d8ce0e3043995da614","tid":1711279,"uid":150609,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:12:13.000Z","msg":"穿越小说 重生之我是习近平<br />\n<br />\n《重生之我是刁大犬》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed2a2d141f127a96d4be9a8fb9979aa6ba15b2e","tid":1711279,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T11:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi